# Keystores and signing material (security-sensitive)
release.jks
*.jks
*.keystore
*.p12
*.pem
*.key
# The shared debug keystore is intentionally committed so that CI and local
# builds use the same signing key, enabling upgrade-in-place installs.
# It only uses the well-known Android debug defaults (storepass/keypass=android)
# and is never used to sign release builds.
!keystore/debug.keystore

